properties.text: As forests are cleared, the remaining vegetation becomes drier and more susceptible to catching fire. Furthermore, excessive cutting down of trees disrupts the forest's natural ability to regulate temperature and humidity, creating conditions that are ripe for wildfires to ignite and spread. Your goal is to use the seed canon to plant a seed that will grow where there is water.
